<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p>This Privacy Policy describes how the <strong>Radhe Radhe Jap Counter</strong> mobile application collects, uses, and protects user information.</p>

<p>By using this application, you agree to the terms described in this Privacy Policy.</p>

