<p>Radhe Radhe Jap Counter is designed to be a simple spiritual counting tool. The app does <strong>not collect personal information</strong> such as your name, email address, or phone number.</p>

<h2>Usage Data</h2>
<p>The app may collect basic anonymous usage data or crash reports to improve app performance and user experience. This information does not personally identify users.</p>

<h2>Local Data Storage</h2>
<p>Your jap counter data (such as count totals) may be stored locally on your device. This information remains on your device and is not transmitted to any server.</p>

<h2>Permissions</h2>
<p>The app may request basic permissions necessary for proper functioning of the application. These permissions are used only for app functionality.</p>

<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>The app may use trusted third-party services such as analytics or advertising providers. These services may collect anonymous data according to their own privacy policies.</p>

<h2>Children’s Privacy</h2>
<p>This application does not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13.</p>

<h2>Security</h2>
<p>We value your trust and strive to protect user data using reasonable security practices.</p>

